__TOC__

* Face to face meet up on Thursday 3rd of September with dinner first in <nowiki>[[http://www.jimmychungs.com/locate/loc_dublin.htm|Jimmy Chungs]]</nowiki> and then onto the <nowiki>[[http://www.thelongstone.com|Longstone]]</nowiki> for drinks. 

* Regular <nowiki>[[https://wiki.ubuntu.com/IrishTeam/IRCMeetings/2009-09-16|Monthly IRC Meeting]]</nowiki> was held at 8pm Irish time on Wednesday 16th September.

* The loco ran a one day conference, <nowiki>[[http://ossbarcamp.com/|OSSBarcamp]]</nowiki> to coincide  with Software Freedom Day on the 19th of September.

* Preparations are well under way for <nowiki>[[https://wiki.ubuntu.com/UbuntuGlobalJam|Global Jam]]</nowiki> next month in <nowiki>[[https://wiki.ubuntu.com/IrishTeam/GlobalJam09|Ireland]]</nowiki>.
